## Tax Loss Harvesting (TLH)

### Pre-Defined Swap Pairs (Wash-Sale Safe)

**Equity:**
- SPY ↔ IVV ↔ VOO ↔ SPLG (S&P 500)
- QQQ ↔ QQQM (Nasdaq 100 — QQQM cheaper at 15bps)
- VEA ↔ IEFA ↔ SPDW (Developed international)
- VWO ↔ IEMG ↔ SPEM (Emerging markets)

**Fixed Income:**
- AGG ↔ BND ↔ SCHZ (US aggregate)
- SGOV ↔ BIL (ultra-short treasury)
- SHV ↔ SPTS (short treasury)
- IEF ↔ VGIT (intermediate)
- TLT ↔ VGLT ↔ SPTL (long treasury)

**Sector/Thematic:**
- ARKK ↔ QQQJ (growth/innovation)
- SIL ↔ SILJ/SLVP (silver miners)
- XME ↔ PICK/GNR (metals & mining)
- SMH ↔ SOXX/XSD (semiconductors)
- IBB ↔ XBI (biotech)

### TLH Workflow

1. Screen positions for unrealized losses > $1,000
2. Identify swap pair from tables above
3. Sell loss lot, immediately buy swap ETF
4. Track 31-day wash sale window cross-account
5. Log harvest: date, ticker sold, ticker bought, loss realized
6. Reference: `tlh_tracker.py` (commands: scan, log, add, harvest)

